
# 📡 Computer Networking Notes

Ye repository mera personal learning journal hai jaha main **Computer Networks** ke topics ko step-by-step padh kar detailed notes (with diagrams) bana raha hu. Har topic ek alag file/folder me milega, jisme concepts ko point-wise aur example ke saath explain kiya gaya hai.

> 🎯 **Goal:** Computer Networks ke fundamentals ko strong karna — OSI/TCP-IP models se lekar Subnetting, Routing aur Application Layer protocols tak.

